The Iguana Vanguard cannot be bought at shipyards, but it is available as one of many [[ownerless ships]].  It can also be [[Buy Used Ship|bought used]].

== Suggested Roles==
The Iguana works well for spacewalk [[boarding]] operations.  Its high speed also allows it to function well on passenger missions, or as a trading ship.

